label.value: glial cell-derived neurotrophic factor receptor signaling pathway involved in ureteric bud formation

value.value: The series of molecular signals generated as a consequence of a glial cell-derived neurotrophic factor receptor binding to one of its physiological ligands that contributes to the formation of the ureteric bud from the Wolffian duct.
